cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IT. 

The paper proposes a neural network approach for perfusion parameter estimation, which involves image analysis and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper uses data augmentation to improve the performance of the neural network, which is a common technique in deep learning and could place the paper in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of regularization in perfusion analysis could also suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with signal processing and estimation, which could place it in cs.IT (Information Theory).
